Ray Gallagher https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ray_Gallagher 0 Ray Gallagher (April 17, 1885 – March 6, 1953) was an American actor of the silent era. He appeared in 95 films between 1912 and 1936. He was born in San Francisco, California and died in Camarillo, California from a heart attack. Ray_Gallagher ( April_17 , 1885 – March_6_,_1953 ) was an_American_actor of the_silent_era .
